This includes creating a university-wide policy on sexual assault and abuse prevention and training a new generation of men and women on what constitutes healthy relationships,โ said Saba Ahmad, executive director of AAFSC, which has a campus office on the UCLA campus.The โA Call To Menโ Project has established itself as one of the most impactful campus prevention programs in the country.
